{"tid":1579613,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"咁多位香港人，你地可唔可以應承我...","createTime":"2019-09-18T15:57:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-09T18:50:07.000Z","uid":62350,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1c1161d3569de0b1e53f33f437a83609d10e691d","tid":1579613,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:57:26.000Z","msg":"老實講，我真係好感動，一開始發起罷工，我都同果班廢老藍絲一樣，質疑佢嘅成效，但自從知道好多小店冒住執粒，俾藍絲罷食嘅風險都企出黎罷工，支持香港人，我先知原來香港仲有好多良心商店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢3個月黎，我見到香港人係會幫手支持同買佢地啲野，更加成功嘅係估唔到可以做到罷食扑野家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以前嘅我淨係識食啲大集團嘅野，例如金拱門，大檸樂，但而家我竟然會寧願特登去好遠嘅小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋發現咗香港原來仲有好多好多好好食嘅野係我地從來都唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位香港人，你地可唔可以應承我<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">永遠都唔好忘記果啲曾經幫過我地嘅良心商店</span>"},{"pid":"34e2e6635f592004383fb7833e67c26cce628b95","tid":1579613,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T15:59:34.000Z","msg":"唔推了，有緣嘅人就會睇到"},{"pid":"3493745fcfc23e06ed2b15033bbba7bd28799302","tid":1579613,"uid":87320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"我幫你推 香港人 加油"},{"pid":"eaf72e3757a7d2909287785dc33afcb1b8098e87","tid":1579613,"uid":146724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:03:16.000Z","msg":"一齊加油 💪🏻"},{"pid":"9e2546f6b90d467530989c99696b396ec28db3b5","tid":1579613,"uid":7270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"加油"},{"pid":"e247697eabf9aedffc5813eb54aa9cf31765d0dc","tid":1579613,"uid":99542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:07:02.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"c11f58ca026dd50b513a764ba07021732709d441","tid":1579613,"uid":235535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:07:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"948484a27f6f7d048e7257a87b6e49ae9ccf9025","tid":1579613,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:08:30.000Z","msg":"可以"},{"pid":"1fd8559b3ac3dd6475530c5b82b3a019ec2c508c","tid":1579613,"uid":32464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:11:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c519c730be3f8c88e500027bada75935513126e5","tid":1579613,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:12:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dd946dbc689f88be92bb2e5017f98709fc5f9b0","tid":1579613,"uid":280475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:12:20.000Z","msg":"Tui"},{"pid":"3f1b9de064aeda7d3e286bb7a8a5b8b0af0b58f7","tid":1579613,"uid":14361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"唔係唔好忘記咁簡單<br />\n我地直頭要扶植呢班黃店<br />\n他日佢地愈開愈多鋪之時，我地就更加聲勢浩大，香港人，係時候改變你地嘅消費習慣啦，盡量將消費轉移到黃店啦！"},{"pid":"25a98e617a8d05bcc631ddd7b16c376a26bfae00","tid":1579613,"uid":293254,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:13:52.000Z","msg":"返樸歸真 <br />\n近十年被大財團蒙蔽 侵蝕香港人思想"},{"pid":"a5ed250bd2c759a717ce8e0f6f27757dd026269e","tid":1579613,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:50:07.000Z","msg":"Thank you<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}